messages.subject: Flickr Japanese History photo group
messages.msgSnippet: I ve created a Japanese history photo group on Flickr, to display photos of historical things and locations in Japan:
messages.messageBody:
I've created a Japanese history photo group on Flickr, to display
photos of historical things and locations in Japan:

http://www.flickr.com/groups/japanesehistory/

If you have a flickr page, and have images of Japan, join up! I'd
like to collect together images of the historic places, temples,
castles, scenery, etc.
